               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Taʾāmmǝra Māryām: I-1) Maṣḥafa śǝrʿāt, The introductory rite of al-Muʿallaqah (fols.
                     5ra-6va)
 I-2) ʾƎsaggǝd laki wa-ʾǝweddǝsaki “I worship Thee…” (fols.

                     6va-7ra)
 I-3) Taʾammǝra Māryām “Miracles of Mary”: 93 miracles (fols.
                     2ra-4vb, 7ra-77ra)
 II) Taʾammǝra Mikāʾel "Miracles of Michael": 1 miracle

                     (fols. 77rb-77vb)
 
 Colophon.</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <locus from="5ra" to="77ra"/>
                     <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2384Taamme">Taʾāmmǝra Māryām "Miracles of Mary"</title>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.1">
                        <locus from="5ra" to="6va"/>
                        <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1968Mashaf">Maṣḥafa śǝrʿāt za-waṣʾa ʾǝm-manbara Mārqos ḥawāryā ʾǝm-makāna maʿāllǝqā</title>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.2">
                        <locus from="6va" to="7ra"/>
                        <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3058RepCh338">ʾƎsaggǝd laki ʾǝsaggǝd laki ʾǝsaggǝd laki wa-ʾǝweddǝsaki</title>
                        <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                     </msItem>
                     
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.3">
                        <locus from="2ra" to="4vb"/>
                        <locus from="7ra" to="77ra"/>
                        <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3585Taamme">Miracles of Mary: 93 miracles</title>
                        
                        
                     </msItem>
                     <colophon xml:id="coloph1"> 
                        <locus from="77ra" to="77rb"/> ዘንቱ፡ ተአምር፡ ዘአጽሐፋ፡ በትግሐቱ፡ አቡነ፡ ገብረ፡ ጊዮርጊስ። በ፵፡
                        ብር። [<cb/>] ተጽሕፈ፡ በዘመነ፡ አቡነ፡ ሊቀ፡ ጳጳሳት፡ አባ፡ ቄርሎስ፡
                        ወብፁዕ፡ ጳጳስ፡ አባ፡ ጴጥሮስ፡ ወበዘመነ፡ ንጉሥነ፡ ምኒልክ፡ በ፶፻{ወ}፭፻፡ ዓመተ፡ ዓለም፡ በ፲ወ፱፻፲ወ፬፡ ዓመተ፡
                        ምሕረት። ዘወሀበቶ፡ ወለተ፡ ሊባኖስ፡ ለመቅደሰ፡ ጰራቅሊጦስ፡ ዘሰረቃ፡ ወዘፈሐቃ፡ ውጉዘ፡ ለይኩን፡ በስልጣነ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡
                        ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ። <note>The colophon states that the Ms. was commissioned by Gabra Giyorgis
                        and donated to the church by Walatta Libānos. It tells that the Ms. was written
                        in <date>1914 year of mercy (= 1921/22 A.D.)</date>, but also refers to King Mǝnilǝk II (r.
                        <date>1889-1913</date>), Patriarch Cyril V of Alexandria (in tenure in <date>1874-1927</date>) and
                        Metropolitan Ṗeṭros (in tenure in <date>1881-1917</date>).</note> </colophon>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
